law student named in court papers as a viable suspect in the 
slayings the sorting could take a month 
stevens has not been charged in the case and he denies any 
involvement his name became public late this week in an affidavit 
supporting a search warrant for two spokane homes used by him 
the affidavit said he was under investigation in the case and 
might be linked to at least 17 other homicide victims whose bodies 
