terrorism and vowed to bring terrorists to justice 
we call on those holding hostages to release them immediately 
and unconditionally and on those with influence over hostagetakers 
to use it to this end the document said there are 15 foreign 
hostages in lebanon including citizens of three summit countries 
the united states britain and italy 
