for the b2 manufactured by northrop corp in palmdale the plane 
will cost about 24 billion over a threeyear peak period beginning 
in fiscal 1992 according to defense department figures 
the department has invested about 224 billion in the plane so 
far 
the pentagon hopes to purchase 132 of the bombers 
