said the sources speaking on condition of anonymity 
the malteseflagged 32000ton puppy was anchored saturday in 
international waters off khor fakkan and several tugboats were to 
be sent to transfer the oil from the leaking tanks the sources said 
khor fakkan a persian gulf port 200 miles south of abu dhabi 
refused to permit the puppy into port because of the leak 
